verses.verse: Praise <S%H1984><s%> ye Jehovah <S%H3050><s%>. Praise <S%H1984><s%>, O ye servants <S%H5650><s%> of Jehovah <S%H3050><s%>, Praise <S%H1984><s%> the name <S%H8034><s%> of Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>.
Blessed <S%H1288><s%> be the name <S%H8034><s%> of Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> From this time forth <S%H6258><s%> and for <S%H5704><s%> evermore <S%H5769><s%>.
From the rising <S%H4217><s%> of the sun <S%H8121><s%> unto the going down <S%H3996><s%> of the same Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>'s name <S%H8034><s%> is to be praised <S%H1984><s%>.
Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> is high <S%H7311><s%> above <S%H7311><s%> all nations <S%H1471><s%>, And his glory <S%H3519><s%> above <S%H7311><s%> the heavens <S%H8064><s%>.
Who is like unto Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> our God <S%H430><s%>, That hath his seat <S%H3427><s%> on high <S%H1361><s%>,
That humbleth <S%H8213><s%> himself to behold <S%H7200><s%> The things that are in heaven <S%H8064><s%> and in the earth <S%H776><s%>?
He raiseth up <S%H6965><s%> the poor <S%H1800><s%> out of the dust <S%H6083><s%>, And lifteth <S%H7311><s%> up the needy <S%H34><s%> from the dunghill <S%H830><s%>;
That he may set <S%H3427><s%> him with princes <S%H5081><s%>, Even with the princes <S%H5081><s%> of his people <S%H5971><s%>.

He maketh the barren woman <S%H6135><s%> to keep <S%H3427><s%> house <S%H1004><s%>, And to be a joyful <S%H8056><s%> mother <S%H517><s%> of children <S%H1121><s%>. Praise <S%H1984><s%> ye Jehovah <S%H3050><s%>.
